name: Nikia Phoenix
bio:
OG freckled model
@darling Society Ambassador (code NIKIAP)

Rep. by @hritalent @scoutmodelagency

social_posts.post_text:
With the shift of the season, and the end of the year near, my body and mind are compelling me to ease up. Most of last week was spent napping. I am basically a house cat adjusting to the cold weather… and I’m okay with that. 
These latest episodes of Reclaiming with Jo + Nikia are all about taking care of self and listening to your spirit. This goes for survivors and those who support us. (That means you too 😌) So please have patience for yourself and patience for me as we ease into this holiday season. Reminding myself that it’s OK to chill out. Healing requires recharging. #selfcare #selflove #wintertime #relax #healing #reclaimingwithjoandnikia #intimatepartnerviolence #survivor

Oh Full Moon in Gemini. The last one of 2022... you speak to me. You begin to put my experiences into perspective, especially since my birthday last year. As much as I pray for patience, I am understanding more and more that the time elapsed allows me to learn the lessons I am meant to know. 
Now that we've got the reflective, philosophical stuff out the way; Universe, you know what's up. Ancestors, you know the deal. Bring it! This Full Moon is in my sign for REASONS.#geminifullmoon #manifest #selflove #innerlight #nikiaphoenix

When we witness violence and experience trauma as children, how does that affect our romantic relationships as adults? Are we more susceptible to abuse if we’ve witnessed abuse? And how do you manifest the life you desire after all this pain? This definitely comes up in the latest episode of Reclaiming with Jo + Nikia with special guest psychologist, author and entrepreneur @_tiffanyshelton. This talk goes in and will hopefully give you hope. Even after all the hurt, you CAN still live the life you desire. 
If you or someone you know is experiencing abuse, resources are available at nikiaphoenix.com. Check out the rest of the conversation wherever you stream podcasts. #domesticviolenceawareness  #healing  #abuse #intimatepartnerviolence #nikiaphoenixpodcast #reclaimingwithjoandnikia #selflove #manifestation

Repeat this affirmation from @_tiffanyshelton daily. When she dropped this gem during our latest podcast about self love and manifesting, it was an a-ha moment. We have limiting beliefs rolling around in our heads that can hold us prisoner. Why are you letting those thoughts live rent-free in your spirit and keep you from what you desire? How can you quiet the self sabotage? Drop a ❤️ and chime in. 
#selflove #manifestation #affirmations #reclaimingwithjoandnikia #tiffanysheltonmariolle #healing #survivor

Raise your hand 🙋🏽‍♀️ if you’ve been blocking your blessings. Currently working through self-limiting beliefs to manifest the love that I want, the life that I want, and so much more. @_tiffanyshelton nailed this and her words are so encouraging. Get out of your own way and make space for abundance. Listen to the whole convo from Reclaiming with Jo + Nikia  wherever you stream podcasts. Let’s get out of our funk and live the life of our dreams. 
#selflove #manifestation #affirmations #reclaimingwithjoandnikia #tiffanysheltonmariolle #healing #survivor #relationshipgoals

social_posts.post_text: When home calls you back and you remember your roots. I promised myself that if I got a chance to see the national champs @gamecockwbb in their element I’d do it. Coach @staley05 is the 🐐 and watching this team play is an honor. I’m witnessing legends in the making. To say I’m a proud Gamecock is an understatement and I don’t take this opportunity for granted. #gogamecocks #proudaluma #ladygamecocks #therealusc

Healing ain’t cute and it doesn’t have to be. Get your tissue out and open yourself up for the ugly cry. It’s a new year, baby . Reset. We are moving through any pain and pushing past the need to be perfect. We are being intentional, staying present, and allowing ourselves to feel all the feels. #healing #uglycry #selflove #inspiration #nikiaphoenixpodcast #reclaimingwithjoandnikia

We’re not gonna mince any words or silence ourselves with this one. State-sanctioned violence against people of color, the LGBTQIA community, and marginalized people is abuse. Reclaiming with Jo +Nikia is coming into 2023 loud and proud with special guest @love.latishia. She does a plethora of awesomeness as a Black queer femme, womanist, writer, facilitator of healing spaces for BIPOC women, femmes, and LGBTQIA folks. Latishia is also a sacral spirituality coach. Hear her words and more on her work concerning gender-based violence and healing. Listen wherever you stream podcasts and share. #domesticviolenceawareness  #healing #abuse #intimatepartnerviolence #nikiaphoenixpodcast #reclaimingwithjoandnikia #lgbtqia #movetoendviolence #abortionrights
#mood

A moment of honesty. I haven’t been feeling like my self, my best self. I’ve been searching for motivation, and although it does come it comes sporadically. Maybe this feeling is seasonal, maybe circumstantial, I just know I’m in it. With all that I do to uplift others, I’m having a time trying to uplift myself. Until this emotional rain stops pouring down on me, I will settle for seconds of sunshine and laughter. I will find my joy again.  #selflove #healing #mentalhealthawareness #survivor #mood #shadowwork

Dear Self, you’ve been wandering in your own wilderness. Those negative thoughts you’ve been having didn’t originate inside of you. Those burdens you picked up are not even your own. That shame doesn’t belong to you. Drop it and free yourself. Your soul may be sore from carrying so much, but allow yourself to stretch and process through the tightness. Be gentle. Be easy. Keep it real. 
I truly appreciate everyone’s kindness. Sometimes it’s so hard to be vulnerable, yet I know that I’m not alone. Thank you. 🙏🏽 #healing #selflove #softlife #trueself

I am finding myself again. I am feeling more like myself again. For months I’d been in a fog. I’d forgotten how much a simple daily ritual like meditation can give my soul some ease. I’m encouraging you to reset and reconnect with yourself by joining my 5-day meditation challenge. Remember that meditation is a practice and it’s not about being perfect. It’s about giving you the time to show yourself grace +self compassion. Check the link in bio to sign up. 🧡 #meditationchallenge #meditatewithnikia #healing #softlife #selflove #meditation #breathe #heartchakra

When you’re surrounded by chaos, it can be a challenge to find the peace within yourself. When you’re in an unsafe situation or constantly facing harm, remember that your innate setting is love. When @love.latishia said these words during a meditation for our podcast, it resonated. Listen to the whole talk wherever you stream podcasts.  Drop a 🧡 and share with someone you know needs it.  #healing  #meditation #selflove #revpleasure #intimatepartnerviolence #nikiaphoenixpodcast #reclaimingwithjoandnikia

I am calling in more good days like this. More lightness. I am committed to loving myself. I am committed to lifting me up. I was tired of feeling low. I am a grown ass woman who likes being silly, soft, sexy and everything in between. Give me more like this. #selflove #healing #selfcare #knowyourworth #grownwoman
You know it when you feel it. You know when it’s been missing. And you know when you do not have the capacity for a substitution. Gimme the light. #healing #selflove #inspiration #heartchakra

Being a creative entrepreneur is some real work. Don’t get it twisted. I’ve got to be self motivated, and at times that can be a real challenge. So how do I get myself in the zone to do what I do? After I meditate, I hit the streets, and find a cute coffee shop like @neighborhood. A matcha and croissant are part of my ritual to get my mind right. I also set goals at the beginning of the week and that helps to keep me focused. How do you get your creative juices flowing? #mondaymotivation #solopreneur #morningswithnikia #teatime #coffeeshop #creativeentrepreneur #blackgirlboss

My encouragement for the week. This affirmation is guiding me through those uncertain moments and reminding me to keep my faith. Speak these words when you need a lift. Carry these words with you. Feel them in your heart. If you start to feel the day getting the best of you, take a break and reaffirm yourself. 🙏🏽 #affirmations #inspiration #morningswithnikia #morningritual

Every kind of love that I know takes commitment. It takes devotion. The love that you have for family, for friends, relationships, and especially self requires dedication and grace. Don’t give up. Put in the time and allow the space for love to move you and let you float. #selflove #inspiration #healing #love #heartchakra #valentinesday #galentinesday

The self discovery is so real. I’ve been back in LA for a few weeks and at times it feels like I’m starting over. This chick has evolved. What is my new relationship to this place and what am I calling in? Instead of reinventing myself, I am remembering that this woman right now is DOPE and she’s always been DOPE. She is 🔥. My higher self is my hype woman.  #selflove #trueself #healing #knowyourworth #inspiration #selflovewithnikia

When the fro is fluffy and the light is hitting you just right, live in that moment. I’ve had too many tired times and frustrating times not to sit in this good feeling. Simmer in it. Soak it up. If you don’t celebrate you and your wins… girl! #selflove #fridayfeeling #blackgirljoy #blessings #healing #affirmations

Hey sunshine. This is your daily reminder to give yourself exactly what you need. Here are 6 simple ways to love yourself right now.
1. Check in with yourself 
2. Stretch especially your neck
3. Give yourself a scalp massage
4. And a hand massage too 
5. Say “I love you”
6. Show gratitude 🙏🏽 

How can you continue to show yourself love? What do you need right now? #selflove #rituals #selfcare #healing #gratitude #nikiaphoenix #freckles #beauty

I’m a long bath and a long shower kind of woman. It’s my time to love on myself and love on my skin. So when I discovered @boucleme has a new body collection that truly nourishes my skin, I had to try. The body wash and body cream are created with intention and natural ingredients like coconut water, cocoa and shea butters. It’s exactly what my skin deserves. Nurturing my body and myself with @boucleme’s new body collection is self care.
 
Drop a heart if you love your skin and use code NIKIA15 for 15% off all Bouclème products including their iconic curl care. #boucleme #selfcare #selflove #loveyourskin #freckles

Storms may have been pounding down on us yesterday, but let these miracles rain down on us today. 
This morning I did what my Granny told me to do before I made this trip. I prayed. I held her fragile yet loving hands while she prayed with me for my safekeeping and encouragement. Her words ring in my spirit. 
May this affirmation carry you through the storms. Say it, share it, and believe it. 🙏🏽#affirmations #encouragement #miracles #gospel #faith #sundayworship

To the women who always have my back. To the ones I admire and adore. You inspire me to keep going. You encourage me to push and stretch myself beyond mental and physical limitations. You believe in me, and I in you. Happy Women’s History Month.
I am so encouraged by the women I connected with @fpmovement’s mat event. When women come together, no force can stop us. #fpmovement #wcw #womenshistorymonth #onesies #healing #wellness

Sundays are that sacred day when we pour into ourselves. We spend time luxuriating and sanctifying the soul. This is our day to love on ourselves so that we can be prepared for the week ahead. So while I gently massage this @keyssoulcare illuminating serum into my skin, I am affirming the light that I am. I shine the brightest when I have compassion for myself. 
What’s your Sunday self care ritual? #longlivesundays #beauty #skincare #freckles #affirmations #keyssoulcare

This moment is for HER. Place one hand over your heart and the other on your womb. Leading up to International Women's Day, I want to draw attention to the parts of us that need extra nurturing. We create with love and passion, so when the heart and the sacral chakras are not balanced, we experience unhappiness, loss of motivation, a decline in sexual energy and more. It is difficult to create life, art, and anything born out of love when the heart and womb are hurting. What do your heart + womb need from you right now? Breathe and listen. If you need require extra help, there's a womb meditation in my 5-day mediation challenge. Sign up and get lifted. #divinefeminine #healing #selflove #meditationmarch #meditatewithnikia #heartchakra #womb

A woman of many faces and many more emotions. A few weeks ago I got the chance to create with @angelamarklew and @bethfollertmakeup. I feel like it’s been forever since I did a beauty shoot, and I was in my head about being out of practice.
When I’m shooting I tap into that expressive being who can switch up facial expressions in a moment from sultry to melancholy to silly. Did I still have the muscles to do it? The juice? Or had I aged out of this thing I love to do? 
While that may sound ridiculous, let’s be real. Society will label a woman old and no longer desirable by the time we reach 30. The fashion and beauty I see for women keeps looking younger and younger, therefore no longer appealing to me. (Oh snap, here comes inspiration.) I’ve got to create something that speaks to women like me. Grown ass women. There’s a void, so let me fill it. *You’re literally reading my brain dump* 
Our needs are evolving as we do, and I want to see more representation for this woman. She is conscious. She travels. She endulges. She likes that soft life. She’s earned the smile lines and the stretch marks. She doesn’t have to put on a good face for anyone. Ahem @im.angelabassett. “Hey Auntie. We love you. ”
She practices self compassion. She is embracing that she is timeless. There’s no expiration date on her brilliance. She will continue to shine. As @michelleyeoh_official said while accepting her Oscar “Ladies, never let anyone tell you you are past your prime.” 
Whew. Okaaaaay! Are you searching for a reflection of the woman you are now and not the girl you used to be? I swear this post had a way different intention yet this is where my spirit guided me. If you stayed til the end, are you ready to build with me? If you’ve been waiting for a sign to speak up or step up, this it. I’m recruiting you. Drop a DM. Drop a heart. Let’s create together. #inspiration #beauty #freckles #grownwoman #selflove #womenshistorymonth #womensupportingwomen

This affirmation is carrying me through this week. I believe the world puts too much pressure on women to be poised and perfect. When faced with disappointment or hurt, putting on a good face can be too much to ask. How can you get over it if you haven’t even acknowledged it? Feel your feelings and allow your emotions to process.  And take as much time as you need. 
Say this affirmation when you need it and share with someone you know needs it too. #affirmations #compassion #healing #selflove #inspiration

OK about that affirmation, here’s the backstory. I recently got passed up for an opportunity 
I really wanted. I felt defeated. I needed the weekend to process my disappointment, and now I’m okay. Acknowledging my feelings and shifting my perspective are making huge differences. So is that affirmation about honoring my feelings. Remember that you can decide when and how you want to proceed once you’ve done the work for yourself. #healing #affirmations #honoryourfeelings #selflove #compassion #inspiration

If you've ever told a mother, auntie or grandmother that she must be lucky, then you know she''ll correct you and say "no baby, I'm blessed." 
We often see the fruit and the reward without realizing all that came together to make something happen for a person. Luck is timing. It's serendipity. The unexplainable.  It's "somebody up there likes me." It's not really luck at all. It's the Divine recognizing our work and our gratitude. Your “pot of gold” is on its way. #blessed #gratitude #luck #divinefavor #divinetiming #inspiration

I absolutely love to read and I realize there are so many books that are still on my list including works by Toni Morrison. She holds a special place in the hearts of many of us. Always imagined she was my professor and mentor in college. 
Anyway, I remember seeing Sula on my mother’s bookshelf when I was a child. I couldn’t touch it then, but I knew it was juicy, the kind of juicy only Toni Morrison knew how to squeeze out. I went looking for Sula in my mom’s collection and I found her last night. I’m whispering as I type because it still feels like my own special secret. So me and Sula are gonna finally have that time to ourselves that I’ve been craving. You’re welcome to read along with me; it’s an unofficial book club I like to call “Books Your Mama Had but you were too young to read them.” Have you read Sula? 
#tonimorrison #womenshistorymonth #booksyourmamahad

As I wash away the self doubt, I am detoxifying my mind from negativity and the unkindness that’s inhabited my inner thoughts. Something was trying to feed on my soul and now I’m reclaiming it. Wash that away. Bathe in compassion. Soak in warmth. Affirm, affirm, affirm. We pray to goddesses, we don’t curse them. #selflove #compassion #healing #affirmations #springawakening #goddess
Rediscovering my happiness, spending time in nature, and enjoying playtime with my inner child. #nature #springtime #selflove #innerchild #healing

Today's affirmation is intended to assist us in waking up to our true selves. You needed to hibernate last season. We all need rest. Give yourself what you need to gradually wake back up. Use this affirmation to remind yourself that there is beauty hiding within you that deserves to be uncovered. #affirmations #springawakening #healing #selflove

Throughout the past month I’ve been experiencing fatigue, resentment, and dissonance. I knew my chakras were out of balance but I wasn’t sure what step I should take first to get back to self.  I tried camel pose and immediately judged myself for not doing it right and being so stiff. Here’s where self compassion comes in. Remember, Self, yoga and meditation are practices. Have the determination to move through the tightness and soreness. Stretch yourself. Open heart, throat, ease the hips. Eventually you will relax into this and feel confident in yourself. You’ll do this pose for real for real. You’re on your way to trusting you again and welcoming courage. 

#selflove #selfcompassion #yoga #healing #meditation

I am choosing to believe that there is something beyond this moment. There is some thing that will bring order to the confusion. It may feel brutal now. yet I believe that the blow will be softened by the reward. You just have to wait for it. I truly believe that there is beauty beyond the chaos. #motivation #inspiration #selfcompassion #patience

With my hair tossled and sleep still in my eyes, I watched the sunrise for the first time in a while this morning. It was as glorious in all the ways one can imagine. The symphony of waves crashing against the shore and soaking my jeans as I witnessed the coming of light. It was what I needed to see to remind me that I am my sun. The calm to the chaos. It’s within me. 

#morningswithnikia #affirmations #sunrise #selflove #beach #inspiration

It is time to expand and call in bigger opportunities, and I need your help to do it. Looking for a few good womxn ( and allies) to join the team and build community. I'm searching for more than contributors, I want collaborators. I want writers, poets, photographers, artists, healers, digital storytellers. If beauty and wellness are your sweet spot, then I need you too. It is my personal mission to build community and strengthen our foundation through inspirational storytelling. Be part of this movement with me. Don't be shy. DM me or shoot me an email and let's talk. Sharing is caring, so please pass this along to someone who's on this wave. XOXO, Nikia #teamnikia #community #selflove #healing #supportblackwomen #womenwriters #artists #wellness

Shine your light. I am searching for a few good humans to join the team and help build community. I want collaborators and partners. Calling in writers, poets, photographers, artists, healers, digital storytellers. If beauty and wellness are your sweet spot, then I need you too. Help me build community and strengthen our foundation through inspirational storytelling. There are important projects dear to me that I need help developing, producing, and bringing to fruition. If this speaks to you, DM me or shoot me an email and let’s talk. Sharing is caring, so please pass this along to someone who fits the vibe. And if you’ve already contacted me, I definitely see you. Thanks for your patience. XOXO, Nikia #teamnikia #community #selflove #healing #supportblackwomen #womenwriters #artists #wellness #beauty

I am proceeding with tenderness. I envelope myself in compassion. When anxiety arises, I place my hand over my heart and whisper to myself “love, love, love.” That beating in my chest means I’m still here and for that I am grateful. 
#selflove #inspiration #compassion #meditation #mantras

Rose petals at her feet. Candles lit and devotions said in her name. She is worshipped. A glance from her can save a life or end it. A mere mortal dare not linger in her presence without falling into a trance. Spellbound. Her wisdom revered. Her presence respected. How soft is her touch yet the memory of her never leaves your skin. She is everlasting. 
I am a goddess. Ethereal. Regal. Divine. Thank you @elizabethmessina for encouraging me to show up for myself as myself for this. @emilyjoymodels, you are timeless.

Images by @elizabethmessina
Goddess workshop @thehybridco 
Beauty by @brushedandblushedhmua 
Gowns by @clairepettibone 
#divinefeminine #elizabethmessina #portraits #selflove #goddess

Repeat after me: I deserve to be soft, to be open, to have my flower watered. 
The morning of this shoot with @elizabethmessina, I felt like my flame had been extinguished. I was sore in my chest. Hips tight. Something within me that needed to die did. What came from that was this: Stop hiding from yourself and settling for the temporary when you desire the everlasting. That will require devotion and faith, and you have that. You are worthy of that. 
Portrait by @elizabethmessina 
Cape by @girlandaseriousdream 

#divinefeminine #elizabethmessina #portraits #selflove #goddess #freckles #flower #softlife #healing #beauty #affirmations

You flourish when you are nurtured. Radiating with warmth when you feel safe. You grow towards the light and do so with vigor and fanfare. Plant yourself in your actual truth, and throw the rest of the bullsh*t out. This is all in love, and I say this with love … Stop shrinking instead of standing tall. Admire your long lines and your angles. The curves and the softness. Take up space. 

Image by @elizabethmessina 
Goddess workshop @thehybridco. 
Beauty by @brushedandblushedmua. Gown by @clairpettibone. 
#divinefeminine #elizabethmessina #portraits #selflove #goddess #bloom #affirmations

Note to self: I am no longer hiding from me. I am no longer sleeping on myself. Even when parts of me want to be invisible, I must use that anxiety. Transmute that anxiety into vulnerability then audacity and bravery. Be bold and do what you want, Nik. What you love! 
Damn I love print but I realize I haven’t been sharing enough of it. So here I am. Not allowing myself to be limited. Image by @xokelleyraye. #selflove #selfcompassion #geminiseason #flourish #nikiaphoenix

What do you need to fly? What do you need to shift from surviving to thriving? As I look through my journal entries from this month, I see something special happening. I wrote that I have the power, the compassion, and the heart to do what I dream. A rare bird. The sky is calling and the heavens are whispering my name. So whathcu gonna do now, Bird?

Image by @xokelleyraye. #selflove #selfcompassion #geminiseason #flourish #nikiaphoenix

Almost forgot to tell you….but Sunday @musewellness_ Hike Club is back again, this time with Guest Host @nikiaphoenix - meditation & reiki master - who will bless us with some meditation at the bamboo forest 🎋

Details: 
RSVP - link is bio - important so we know who’s in our hiking crew. 
When - Sunday - June 4th @ 1pm - we head down the trail by 1:15
Where - East Palisade Indian Trail 
Destination - Bamboo Forest 
Parking - Parking is limited to arrive earlier and consider carpooling. 
Snacks - bring water and snacks for the end of our hike, trust me you’ll want them. 
Journal - bring something to write with 
Who - friends, kids, dogs welcome - most of us are creatives, NOT pro-athletes, and looking for people to get into nature and have new experiences with.

In nature I feel free and connected to something bigger than myself. I feel grounded with Her. This Sunday with @musewellness_  Hike Club I am honored to guide you in meditation and intention setting. We’ll take a nature walk and then get nestled in the bamboo forest for meditation. Bring a journal, water, snacks, and an open heart. It’s happening Sunday June 4 1pm in ATL. RSVP with link in bio so we know who’s in the squad. 🌿 #hikeclub #musewellness #meditation #nature #meditatewithnikia

As a teenager, I really wanted to be a DJ. Amongst my friends, I even had a moniker, DJ Nikki Rock. She can still rock the block trading in turntables and a gold chain for her laptop and matcha. 😎 In honor of my birthday (June 10) and Black Music Month, I’m sharing the Geminis that have created the soundtrack to my life. These are songs that evoke memories and make you feel something. This playlist is Black and Grown… and ever-changing. It’s the Gemini way. Submitting this for your audible pleasure… link in bio. #geminiseason #birthdayplaylist #blackmusicmonth #weekendplaylist #djnikkirock #rebirth

It’s giving Phoenix. She on fiyah! I wanted to fly into a new year with vibrancy and motion. Burn, baby, burn. I call it a rebirth. 
Fresh color, trim, and style by @jerriansari. 
#rebirth #geminiseason #nikiaphoenix #naturalhair #curlyhair #redhead #freckles #blackgirlwithfreckles #hairinspo

Acknowledge the light within you. This Summer Solstice tap into your inner sun, your solar plexus. When this chakra is out of alignment, we are unsure of ourselves and our power. We experience rejection, digestive issues, and anger. Yet when we are balanced, we shine bright and know our purpose in this life. Remember you are a sun. Listen to the full meditation by following the link in bio. ☀️#summersolstice #meditatewithnikia #solarplexus #healing #meditation #selflove

Over the weekend my hair was touched without my permission. It’s taken me a while to process. I felt powerless and disrespected. My hair was touched by a complete stranger, a white woman, and I am thoroughly aware of all the cultural and racial implications that go along with this. I had to consider all of that in my response to her.  I could only defend myself with my words... and I was the only one defending me. I told her “ I am not your pet. I am a human being.  You must ask for my consent and I would still tell you no because I do not belong to you.” The grace, dignity, and restraint it took to contain my anger, because no matter what I’d be viewed as the angry Black woman. Incidents like this ignite my social anxiety. I did not feel safe and I did not feel protected. Only today have I been able to articulate and begin to release all the emotions I’d been holding on to.  In between hurt and tears, I journal and soothe myself. I give myself what I need. I tell myself that I am a human being. I belong to me. My hair is my own. I am safe. I am protected. I am powerful. I am at peace. 
#selflove #healing #naturalhair #afro #donttouchmyhair #microagressions #blackgirlbeautiful #affirmations #racialtrauma

Here’s the tea: I am committed to this life, my health, my wellbeing. My solar plexus said “girl, we gotta get right,” so I’m spending time in the sun and with my number one cat. No toxicity here. #selfcare #selflove #softlife #summerbaby #teatime

She is me. I am in a stage of softening. Opening. Allowing. I am longing for… and want to be yearned for. Not this unrequited love. It’s reciprocated. Respected. Adored. Sultry. Thick like molasses. 
#selflove #grownwoman #softlife #divinefeminine

In delicate gloves. A bit undone. Soft light. The day of this shoot I wrote in my journal “I am releasing doubts and grounding myself in self compassion.” Release can take a long time. But when it’s done and you’re stretching like a cat waking up from a long nap, you know you are yourself again. You’ve shed the heaviness and are free to be wild again. 

Image by @elizabethmessina
Beauty by @brushedandblushedhmua 

#divinefeminine #elizabethmessina #beauty #selflove #selfcompassion  #portrait #freckles #naturalhair

I am listening now. My body was definitely trying to tell me something and finally it screamed. All my chakras were out of balance. Solar plexus, sacral, heart, root. You name it. When your solar plexus is imbalanced, you may experience feelings of rejection, powerlessness, digestive issues. And yes this has rung true for a while. The process of feeling this new thing out, releasing, and resetting is challenging yet I’m so thankful for guidance from my friends @musewellness_ and @wildlingnutrition. Self Love is my mantra, but what does it really mean? A while ago my friend @asiamdav of @diefreestudios encouraged me to use mind mapping to define Self Love. Fast forward to a thought that came to me in the shower today:
Maybe your body is tired. Maybe it just doesn’t have it today. Maybe your heart isn’t in it, and that’s okay. Maybe your mind can’t settle or maybe the mental clarity isn’t in your grasp. It’s all fine. You’re going to be okay. Grant yourself the grace you need. Feel what you need to feel, so that one day soon you can be who you know you truly are. Self love cannot exist without self compassion.
If this resonates drop a ❤️and share with someone who needs it. #selflove #selfcompassion #healing #kindness

This week I am reminding myself to practice gratitude and savor moments. There are times I feel like I’m running and not slowing down to be truly appreciative of those “micro joys” as my fellow @thelola_women member and sunshine facilitator @dayle.bennett says. 
Every day, twice a day actually, I journal about what I’m grateful for… the things that bring me joy. And today I’m sharing them with you. I am always so grateful for my cat. He reminds me to be here. I am grateful for nourishment.  I am grateful for moments with self. And I am grateful for moments in community that remind me I’m not alone. I’m grateful for the birds that I heard on my morning walk. 
You know, I can keep going and that’s what’s so beautiful about gratitude. It’s contagious. 🙏🏽 What are you grateful for?

Before this year is behind me, I want to recognize the woman that I am becoming. The woman that is not like she was yesterday and still evolving. I need to mourn who I thought I was. I’ve been tired, a bit lost, and hiding somewhere in the shadows. At times I’ve felt defeated and silenced. To act like everything‘s been coming up roses would mean denying all that I’ve experienced and all that I’ve been feeling. So I acknowledge those emotions and those sensations, and yet in the same breath, I can still acknowledge the light. My light. Because it’s the light that has kept me here and it is the light that will lead me toward a new horizon. For all of that, the sour, the gritty and the pretty, I am grateful to be here. This is me. 

Image by @angelamarklew with beauty by @bethfollertmakeup. #selfove #healing #cleanbeauty #gratitude #freckles #becoming  #radicalselflove #beauty
